{"tid":2181231,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)阿比與阿弟1-3","createTime":"2020-08-30T12:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T18:06:51.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"01e693e2e41bd2cb52311c378abdd335b4205bdd","tid":2181231,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T12:29:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoBjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=1f568033\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoBjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=8969cdaa\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoBjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=e452d637\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/6/6d/Bill_%26_Ted%27s_Excellent_Adventure_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F6%2F6d%2FBill_%2526_Ted%2527s_Excellent_Adventure_Poster.jpg&h=c1d63aab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/c/cc/Bill_%26_Ted_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fc%2Fcc%2FBill_%2526_Ted_2.jpg&h=f0f8287f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/2020061105.jpg?crop=0.502xw:1.00xh;0,0&amp;resize=640:*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fhmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2F2020061105.jpg%3Fcrop%3D0.502xw%3A1.00xh%3B0%2C0%26resize%3D640%3A%2A&h=2500dbbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.《阿比與阿弟的冒險》講述一對高中生為了完成學校的歷史作業，受到未來人的幫忙，得以用電話亭外型的時光機，去收集歷史人物，在禮堂為他們進行口頭報告。收集的過程中笑話與冒險百出，最後順利完成報告並交到來自於中古世紀的女友<br />\n<br />\n2.續集《阿比與阿弟暢遊鬼門關》，則延續了首集的設定。兩位主角在未來所組的樂團音樂，可以拯救世界讓天下太平，所以想統治世界的魔王，派出兩個外型與他們相同的機器人，前去殺了他們，為的是改變歷史。而被機器人殺死的阿比與阿弟面對死神，卻以詭計擊敗死神，進行一個復活重生、打倒機器人，以挽回歷史的行動<br />\n<br />\n3.比爾（阿比）與泰德（阿弟）現在忍受著中年人的單調生活。直到來自未來的訪客前來警告他們，他們需要在78分鐘內創作一首歌曲，這將挽救地球和整個宇宙的生命。這使兩人再次利用時光機器來與家人、老友、著名音樂家一起工作，以共同完成任務<br />\n<br />\n9 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoBjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=fa87cd3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoBjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=4cbeb782\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46435dbd5c1d5e128937154e6115e98e358761bb","tid":2181231,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T12:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0471de3852b91a8c405b6f21b1ccc051727b07bd","tid":2181231,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7753be5a578a90a58a87c91d56eaf9d1167f7fd5","tid":2181231,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T16:23:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"816e45ee97e8bb4f74a0436877b7c1251a77a9b2","tid":2181231,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T18:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}